sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Swift as Swift SDK
    participant ClaudeSDK as ClaudeCodeSDK
    participant NodeJS as Node.js SDK
    participant DirectCLI as Direct CLI
    participant PythonSDK as Python SDK

    Note over Dev,PythonSDK: ATTEMPT 1: Direct Anthropic Swift SDK

    Dev->>Swift: Import SDK, call messages API
    Swift--xDev: FAILED: Requires ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
    Note right of Swift: Claude Code uses OAuth,<br/>no API key available

    Note over Dev,PythonSDK: ATTEMPT 2: ClaudeCodeSDK (Official Swift)

    Dev->>ClaudeSDK: Integrate with Vapor backend
    ClaudeSDK->>ClaudeSDK: FileHandle.readabilityHandler<br/>+ Combine PassthroughSubject
    ClaudeSDK--xDev: FAILED: Silent -- RunLoop/NIO mismatch
    Note right of ClaudeSDK: Vapor NIO never pumps RunLoop<br/>Publisher emissions vanish

    Note over Dev,PythonSDK: ATTEMPT 3: JS @anthropic-ai/sdk via Node.js

    Dev->>NodeJS: Spawn Node subprocess
    NodeJS--xDev: FAILED: Same API key problem
    Note right of NodeJS: Plus 800ms Node.js<br/>cold start overhead

    Note over Dev,PythonSDK: ATTEMPT 4: Direct Claude CLI subprocess

    Dev->>DirectCLI: Process() with GCD stdout reading
    DirectCLI->>DirectCLI: Detects CLAUDECODE=1 in env
    DirectCLI--xDev: FAILED: Nesting detection blocks execution
    Note right of DirectCLI: Works standalone,<br/>fails inside CC session

    Note over Dev,PythonSDK: SOLUTION: Python Agent SDK wrapper

    Dev->>PythonSDK: Strip env vars + spawn python3 sdk-wrapper.py
    PythonSDK->>PythonSDK: claude_agent_sdk.query()<br/>with include_partial_messages
    PythonSDK-->>Dev: SUCCESS: NDJSON stream via stdout
    Note right of PythonSDK: Inherits OAuth auth,<br/>clean async iterator,<br/>2-3s warm latency
